# Frontend

Next.js App Router. Functional components + custom hooks. Keep components small and colocated under `components/`.

## Design tokens (from Stitch)

Use the Tailwind tokens ported from `stitch_reel_ai_movie_assistant/cinematic_intelligence_system/DESIGN.md` — the noir + gold palette (`surface #17130d`, `primary #ffd185`, `primary-container #e8b457`), Playfair Display (headlines) + Inter (UI), and the defined radii/spacing.

- **No hardcoded hex** in components — reference Tailwind theme tokens (`bg-surface`, `text-primary`, etc.).
- Fonts via `next/font` (Inter, Playfair Display); Material Symbols for icons.

## Data & auth

- Supabase client for auth (login/session); attach the JWT to backend calls.
- A single typed API client (`lib/api.ts`) for the backend, including the SSE stream from `/chat`. No scattered `fetch` calls in components.
- Type all props and API responses; no `any`.

## Structure

- Routes in `app/`: landing (`page.tsx`), `(auth)/login`, `chat/`.
- Reusable pieces (`Sidebar`, `ChatThread`, `MessageBubble`, `CitationChip`, `SourcesPanel`, `GraphPanel`, `ChatInput`) in `components/`.
